    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="635486807">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-635486807" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-635486807" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="635486807">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yukiyuko/">口袋_肥力士</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-02-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">比起认识你自己这个名字，Freedom From the Known大概更能概括本书内涵。真正的自由是什么，大概认识快感，恐惧之后重新对人生的理解才是自由</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="473942016">
        <div class="comment">
